    <item>
      <title>中国将重点放在产业政策上，跳过大规模需求刺激</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-13/china-sets-industrial-policy-as-top-economic-priority-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高领导人誓言要把产业政策作为明年经济的首要任务。这一消息可能会让那些希望出台更多以消费者为中心的刺激措施的投资者感到失望。约翰·刘 (John Liu) 在彭博电视台 (Bloomberg Television) 上有更多报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-13/china-sets-industrial-policy-as-top-economic-priority-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 00:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界上最贫穷国家的债务不足 3.5 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-13/debt-crisis-poorest-nations-owe-trillions-in-high-interest-rate-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街鼓励非洲、拉丁美洲和亚洲国家借贷。现在持续的高利率可能会刺激 2024 年的清算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-13/debt-crisis-poorest-nations-owe-trillions-in-high-interest-rate-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 00:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国准备注入现金以补充流动性、促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/china-may-look-to-pump-more-cash-with-mlf-loans-to-spur-more-liquidity-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计中国央行本周将通过政策性贷款向金融体系注入更多现金，以应对部分因大规模债券发行而导致的流动性紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/china-may-look-to-pump-more-cash-with-mlf-loans-to-spur-more-liquidity-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
